{"tid":411068,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"UBI：《薩爾達》借鑒了我們的遊戲","createTime":"2017-09-23T13:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T11:20:13.000Z","uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":182,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e505b1f5156a16d9c2a17127941732090ee21114","tid":411068,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkgnews.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Yves-Guillemot.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgnews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F02%2FYves-Guillemot.jpg&h=12395b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《塞爾達傳說》系列無疑是任天堂最為成功，乃至遊戲圈最為舉足輕重的遊戲，最新Switch平台的《塞爾達傳說：荒野之息》同樣如此，不過育碧CEO近日做客《Edge》雜誌宣稱，其實《塞爾達傳說：荒野之息》借鑒了他們的遊戲，尤其是他們的沙盒遊戲，比如《Far Cry》系列，一起來了解下。<br />\nYves Guillemot通過《Edge》雜誌採訪表示，《塞爾達傳說：荒野之息》與《地平線：黎明時分》這類新遊戲借鑒了很多育碧遊戲，尤其是育碧沙盒遊戲就有的概念設計元素，比如《Far Cry》、《刺客教條》、《看門狗》系列，然後將其轉化為他們自己的遊戲。<br />\n&ldquo;這其實挺有意思的，因為《塞爾達傳說：荒野之息》借鑒了很多《Far Cry》系列與其他育碧遊戲就有的設計元素，不過他們做的挺不錯的。&rdquo;Yves Guillemot說道， &ldquo;我覺得重點不是他們做的遊戲系統，而是他們可以做到這麼完美，讓玩家體驗到最棒的遊戲體驗。&rdquo;<br />\n雖然遊戲可以藉鑑其他遊戲，但將其開發為協調的遊戲體驗最為關鍵，所以育碧聚焦將他們的遊戲打造的多元化，吸引遊玩。<br />\n&ldquo;不過我們的遊戲花了大量功夫，讓每款遊戲都不同與彼此。這一直都是我們的宗旨，但是你看這些市場上的新遊戲，甚至是索尼的最新作品《Horizon Zero Dawn》,他們都採用了與我們遊戲相同的遊戲系統，因為這個業界，我們總是去觀察其他的遊戲，其他的遊戲廠商。&rdquo;<br />\n面對這樣的情況，Yves Guillemot表示，育碧開始著重關注以及開發多人遊戲作品，比如《榮耀戰魂》、《全景封鎖》、《Rainbow Six: Siege》就是如此，當然育碧仍然會繼續探索遊戲業界的多元化設計。<br />\n育碧接下來關注單機元素的遊戲包括《刺客教條：起源》，以及明年發售的《Far Cry 5》與《South Park》新作。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkgnews.com/41963/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgnews.com%2F41963%2F&d=JKh%2BUJ3vdBTNOyz78cyjaFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=a9cf1df6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkgnews.com/41963/</a>"},{"pid":"0047aa6f769b4094ad2c4a031f39acd43e72f1dc","tid":411068,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcb1753cad300d8ced42ab5aae01b4fcb92986b","tid":411068,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"佢又講得出口"},{"pid":"20093ad73fe738b33a7141c26a72c04041d3f0b0","tid":411068,"uid":8636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"佢啲open world game有無借鑒GTA3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493127c66d58d41165d6270d9eb00dc253241170","tid":411068,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢喇 記得食埋你地啲薯仔server<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41b88ed8f78ed03defada6409c174ddc0ba9a32","tid":411068,"uid":93190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:37:39.000Z","msg":"真係唔怕醜"},{"pid":"7bfa704e73d74b8f99708a9edfb05894e9ce7fa0","tid":411068,"uid":392,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T13:50:32.000Z","msg":"講出黎唔怕醜果下犀利"},{"pid":"82052ef31a59e0d6107e0878736bdb13033c8f02","tid":411068,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:01:12.000Z","msg":"遊戲界三叔"},{"pid":"6f28e98e1ec9d1b81427f7a7193db9a2c38317a3","tid":411068,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"萬年引擎"},{"pid":"28b31fb6b41540046d2d8aabee46598c61ac9515","tid":411068,"uid":59480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"虧佢講得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces